@startuml Sequence_N8NNotification
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10

title Sequence Diagram: Notifikasi Otomatis via N8N

participant "GPS Device" as Device
participant "Backend\nLocation API\n(Express)" as BE
participant "Geofence\nDetection\nLogic" as Logic
participant "N8N\nWebhook\nEndpoint" as N8N
participant "N8N\nWorkflow" as N8NFlow
participant "Email\nService" as Email
participant "Telegram\nBot" as Telegram
participant "WhatsApp\nAPI" as WhatsApp
participant "User\nNotification" as User
participant "MongoDB\nNotificationLog" as DB

Device -> BE: POST /api/location\n{\n  deviceId,\n  latitude,\n  longitude,\n  accuracy,\n  speed\n}

activate BE
  BE -> Logic: Cek apakah point\ndalam geofence

  Logic -> Logic: Ray Casting\nAlgorithm

  alt Violation Detected
    Logic --> BE: isViolation = true\nviolatedGeofences = [...]

    BE -> BE: Kumpulkan webhook\npayload:
    note right of BE
      {
        vehicleId: "...",
        vehicleName: "Tesla",
        location: {lat, lng},
        geofenceId: "...",
        geofenceName: "Zone A",
        violationTime: "...",
        speed: "...",
        userId: "..."
      }
    end note

    BE -> N8N: Trigger POST\nN8N Webhook URL\ndengan payload

    activate N8N
      N8N -> N8NFlow: Terima webhook\ndi N8N Workflow

      activate N8NFlow
        N8NFlow -> N8NFlow: Parse webhook\npayload

        par Email Notification
          N8NFlow -> Email: Send email to\nuser.email\nSubject: Geofence Violation Alert\nBody: Vehicle has left Zone A
          activate Email
            Email -> Email: Format template\nemail
            Email -> User: Kirim email\nnotification
            User --> Email: Email diterima
          deactivate Email

        and Telegram Notification
          N8NFlow -> Telegram: Send message ke\nuser.telegramChatId\nvia Telegram Bot API
          activate Telegram
            Telegram -> User: Kirim notification\ndi Telegram Chat
            User --> Telegram: Terima pesan
          deactivate Telegram

        and WhatsApp Notification
          N8NFlow -> WhatsApp: Send message ke\nuser.whatsappPhone\nvia WhatsApp Business API
          activate WhatsApp
            WhatsApp -> User: Kirim notifikasi\ndi WhatsApp
            User --> WhatsApp: Terima pesan
          deactivate WhatsApp
        end par

        N8NFlow -> DB: Log notification\nstatus = "sent"
        activate DB
          DB -> DB: Create\nNotificationLog:\n{\n  vehicleId,\n  geofenceId,\n  userId,\n  channel: "email|telegram|whatsapp",\n  status: "sent",\n  sentAt: now()\n}
          DB --> N8NFlow: Success
        deactivate DB

        N8NFlow -> N8N: Return response\nstatus: "success"
      deactivate N8NFlow

    N8N --> BE: Return 200 OK
    deactivate N8N

    BE -> DB: Buat LocationLog\ndengan isViolation=true
    BE -> BE: Buat Response:
    note right of BE
      {
        success: true,
        isViolation: true,
        violatedGeofences: [...],
        notificationsSent: true
      }
    end note

  else No Violation
    Logic --> BE: isViolation = false

    BE -> DB: Buat LocationLog\ndengan isViolation=false

    BE -> BE: Buat Response\nisViolation: false
  end

  BE --> Device: Return response
deactivate BE

note over N8N, N8NFlow
  N8N Workflow Configuration:
  1. Webhook node untuk trigger
  2. Condition node untuk check
  3. Send Email node
  4. Send Telegram node
  5. Send WhatsApp node
  6. Database logging node

  Keuntungan N8N:
  - Decoupling: Sistem tidak tergantung
    pada email/Telegram client
  - Scalability: N8N handle queue
  - Flexibility: Mudah ubah
    logic tanpa redeploy backend
end note

note over Email, WhatsApp
  Multi-channel notification:
  - Email: Formal, detail
  - Telegram: Real-time, chat-based
  - WhatsApp: Personal phone, urgent

  User dapat configure channel
  di profile preferences
end note

@enduml
